description:
You asked for it so we had to give it! Gennaros bolognese, this is one hell of a recipe that is worth every minute of love, care, and attention. Give it a go, you wont be disappointed! 

Gennaro in Italy
Over the coming months we will be posting a series of Gennaros recipes from Italy, some of which you, the audience, have specifically asked for and others are Gennaro doing what the Italians do best  sourcing good ingredients and making simple, bold dishes with little effort and time involved. 

Rather than cut these videos right down, we have left them a little longer and kept them relaxed. We think watching Gennaro in Italy is a glorious thing, and Gennaro does such a great job at being both inspiring and entertaining. So sit back and enjoy these as they roll out  we would love to know what you think.
